                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7402" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0742</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6132 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">锲而不舍：爱靠谱的社会创业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Aikaopu&#39;s persistent way of social entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱世峰，俞浩萍，胡文静，李晶华，沈玺洲，郭亦昕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波财经学院*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波爱靠谱网络信息服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会创业 ；社会创业机会识别；社会创业商业模式；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">social entrepreneurship, social entrepreneurship opportunity identification, social entrepreneurship business model, sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了原浙江围海集团任人力资源总监龚青春看到部分适婚青年因遇到不良婚恋网站或中介受到的情感挫伤和财物损失，进而导致企业因职工婚恋问题而人才流失情况。为更好的帮助了让有结婚意愿的大龄青年或适婚青年快速有效的找到幸福，为企业留住人才，为社会构建和谐，决定创办“爱靠谱”公益职场红娘平台，从根本上杜绝一些网络相亲平台上酒托、饭托、已婚者等社交乱相。面对社会创业过程中的可持续发展问题，龚青春创新商业模式，以信息化工具和专业化运作赋能公益平台，使企业得到迅速发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">this case describes the social reality that Mr Gong Qingchun, the former human resources director of Zhejiang Weihai group, saw scam websites or intermediaries, which has led to the brain drain of enterprises due to employee marriage problems, and it even leads the brain drain caused by employees&#39; marriage problems in enterprises. In order to help older youths who are willing to get married to match couples and achieve sustainable development, find happiness for individuals, retain talents for enterprises, build harmony for society and open source for China&#39;s human resources industry, Mr Gong decided to create the Aikaopu public welfare workplace matchmaker platform.This platform takes enterprises and institutions’ trade unions, Youth League committees and human resources practitioners of enterprises and institutions as the link points, to ensure the data is authenticity and reliability , fundamentally put an end to the social disorder of wine trays, dinner trays and married people online scamming.Facing these difficulties in the process of social entrepreneurship, Mr Gong innovated the business model, enabled matchmaker this traditional industry with information-based tools and professional operation, therefore Aikaopu could develop rapidly.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会创业;社会创业的社会环境;社会创业动机;社会创业机会识别过程;社会创业的商业模式和社会创业的可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-07</td>
                            </tr>
